{
  "stem": "8753.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She always was a fighter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Lack, L-A-C-K.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Lack, a working camp.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she went to that town, and she tried to talk to some people who got contacts with the leaders from the camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was understood that he will be freed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Again, she paid some money to these people, and it was understood that-- she, like, bribing them-- that he will be freed.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And a day before, he was hit over his-- over the head with a metal-- with a metal something.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bar or something.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was killed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he died, and then my sister really was falling apart.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Lonya's sister and father went to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my mother used to bring them food very often.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were very distraught, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- and she used to help.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was-- and Matl.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She used to help them sometimes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, we came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had enough food, so didn't starve.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And other people already were starving, because in the city, people would make a living from each day they, you know, they-- they used to hunt, and that's how they make their money.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in the ghetto, they used to give out-- there was a Judenrat in the ghetto, and they used to give rations, bread of whatever.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But of course, it was-- they were very small rations.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "People couldn't survive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And people died daily, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember that sight-- I never forget-- two people, two men, would pull a wagon with the corpses on the wagon.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They used to collect the-- in other words, the Germans ordered the Jews to pick up the corpses.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Instead of have a horse and buggy pull the wagon, they made the Jews pull the wagon.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, there was only a wire fence.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
